org.mule.modules.salesforce.apex.antlr

Interface JavaListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApexRestBaseListener, JavaBaseListener

    public interface JavaListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by JavaParser.
